{"tid":1580494,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲阿德萊德保護區清出大量針筒引居民擔憂","createTime":"2019-09-19T06:03:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T06:54:55.000Z","uid":50745,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"82bc60bc59e8518f1d2982a6f130bad890ba518d","tid":1580494,"uid":50745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T06:03:45.000Z","msg":"驚嚇啊......<br />\n<br />\n近日，阿德萊德南區一處保護區發現了大約60支注射器，當地居民對此感到十分憤怒。<br />\n<br />\n在9月14日的例行檢查中，當地清理組織在太陽眼鏡盒和膠樽中發現了危險的針筒。照片被發佈在Facebook上後，引發了網民的憤怒，人們擔心可能有人被扎傷。<br />\n<br />\n志願者Zane Gough表示，雖然她確實預計到會些發現，但她沒想會在這麼小的區域中找到那麼多的針筒。最近幾個月，在附近海域也發現了大量的注射器，情況令人擔憂。<br />\n<br />\n非牟利組織「Our Coast，Our Mission」和「Adopt a Spot」每星期對Onkaparinga流域進行一次搜索清理。<br />\n<br />\n成員Chris Lemar表示，收集到的物品中最危險的就是被丟棄的針管，在該地區數量如此之多的發現令他們感到震驚。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/5097277-%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B2%E9%98%BF%E5%BE%B7%E8%90%8A%E5%BE%B7%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%B7%E5%8D%80%E6%B8%85%E5%87%BA%E5%A4%A7%E9%87%8F%E9%87%9D%E7%AD%92-%E5%BC%95%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E6%93%94%E6%86%82?current_cat=6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fhongkong%2Farticle%2F5097277-%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E9%2598%25BF%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E8%2590%258A%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E4%25BF%259D%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E5%258D%2580%25E6%25B8%2585%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2587%258F%25E9%2587%259D%25E7%25AD%2592-%25E5%25BC%2595%25E5%25B1%2585%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%2593%2594%25E6%2586%2582%3Fcurrent_cat%3D6&d=gqDWnnaI%2FM4dwC7GJUFj5SK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=55bd5379\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/5097277-%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B2%E9%98%BF%E5%BE%B7%E8%90%8A%E5%BE%B7%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%B7%E5%8D%80%E6%B8%85%E5%87%BA%E5%A4%A7%E9%87%8F%E9%87%9D%E7%AD%92-%E5%BC%95%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E6%93%94%E6%86%82?current_cat=6</a>"},{"pid":"71c28287a17a45b6098f87de97029fa0c2c68228","tid":1580494,"uid":50745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T06:05:22.000Z","msg":"<